author: krishna
title: Ingredients
process: 1)Heat the oil in a non-stick kadhai and add the cumin seeds.
2)When the seeds crackle, add the asafoetida and sauté on a medium flame for a few seconds.

3)Add the yellow moong dal, turmeric powder, coriander-cumin seeds powder, chilli powder, salt and 1 cup of water, mix well and cover and cook on a medium flame  for 10 minutes, while stirring occasionally.
4)Remove from the flame, add the coriander and mix well.
ingredients: 8 tablespoon unsalted butter, at room temperature
